if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後個晚 我叫呀媽幫我洗返手巾仔 佢話呀仔 做咩條手巾咁多血 你整傷左呀 我話無事 雖然好痛 但仲好暖心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n唉 真係戀愛啦 個日我報左a0  佢仲對我笑笑口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"之後個晚 我叫呀媽幫我洗返手巾仔 佢話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呀仔</span></span> 做咩條手巾咁多血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0400b49c7e30f38cacdf9dae248726856e5947c1","tid":782883,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦ching 你出哂名臭雞"},{"pid":"d35a963ef88fe698a14c670b34dff8860f7d6cd3","tid":782883,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"想屌醒樓主"},{"pid":"6fa75da8a9fa91b479210257a8d5f0f55f13fc54","tid":782883,"uid":172925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第一屆吹水大會</span></span>"},{"pid":"600391372db036dbd2796d7a9b1063a9292a1902","tid":782883,"uid":198943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"走啦假膠"},{"pid":"861fb720947ae24caa3dc2a1944eb107a51d85a1","tid":782883,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ef3b95a962b70ff3059e699b09a1d718cf618e4","tid":782883,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"大家都溝人 點解你個po會無咁多負皮<img src=\"/asse